      <title>对冲基金在选举前抛售日元 导致日本风险激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/hedge-funds-sold-yen-just-before-election-catapulted-japan-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本执政党自民党在议会大选中失利的前一周，对冲基金转而看跌日元，有可能导致日元跌势进一步扩大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/hedge-funds-sold-yen-just-before-election-catapulted-japan-risk</guid>
